us in the region and recommended annulling the census to hold a new version in  the government sought an assessment by international experts before making a final decision the team which included three experts that represented the world bank and the eu statistics commission found “no basis for doubting the usability of the census data for most if perhaps not all of the customary uses and recommended its release subject to the elimination of the imputation of housing units not observed on the ground during the enumeration and the concurrent publication of a methodological and administrative report statisticsedit gdp compositionedit main macroeconomic aggregates of gdp aggregate  millions of clp   change yearonyear  private consumption    government consumption    changes in inventories   — gross fixed capital formation    exports    imports    exports minus imports   — gdp    note data are preliminary source cuentas nacionales de chile – evolución de la actividad económica en el año  p  central bank of chile accessed on  march  gdp by sectoredit gross domestic product by sector of the economy sector  millions of clp  agriculture and forestry   fishing   mining copper other       manufacturing industry foodstuff beverage and tobacco textile clothing and leather wood and furniture cellulose paper and printing oil refinement chemical rubber and plastic nonmetallic mineral products and basic metals metallic products machinery equipment and others                     electricity gas and water   construction   retail   restaurants and hotels   transportation   communications   financial services   business services   real estate services   personal services health education and other services   public administration   gdp at factor cost   vat taxes   import duties   gdp at market prices   note  data are preliminary source cuentas nacionales – evolución de la actividad económica en el año  p  central bank of chile accessed on march   top exportsedit chiles exports in – chil